HEADWORD: Gainsborough hat
<hw>Gains"borough hat</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A woman's broad-brimmed
hat of a form thought to resemble those shown in portraits by
<person>Thomas <etsep>Gainsborough</etsep></person>, the English artist
(1727-88).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

